criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — identified context, options, and stakeholders ("we have some information... alternatives"); 
Represent — described building a Python model and inputs/toggles ("planned Python model... inputs I feed in"); 
Implement — ran scenarios and reported numeric outputs (EPS, ownership changes) and noted a code run ("I implement the model and here's what the numbers told me"); 
Validate/Reflect — compared value creation vs transfer and produced a reasoned hybrid recommendation ("Reflecting on all factors, my recommendation is a hybrid approach").
